parameters.toolDescription:
Loads the full property record, session, transfer history, and existing extractions from the database.
Call this before calling Title Attorney. Pass the returned data in the Title Attorney call.
Input: { property_id }
Output: { property, session, appraiser_transfer_history, extractions }

